  <div class="content">
    <h2>Disabled buttons</h2>

    <p>To create disabled buttons, you can either add the class <code>button__disabled</code> to the button, or alternatively you can use <code>disabled</code> attribute on the button to get the styling without having to worry about classes.</p>
  </div>

