  <div class="content">
    <h2>Icons</h2>

    <p>Icons inside buttons can be controlled with various helper classes.</p>

    <p><code>button__icon-left</code> can be used for buttons with text an icon to the left.</p>
    <p><code>button__icon-right</code> can be used for buttons with text an icon to the right.</p>
    <p><code>button__icon</code> can be used for buttons with no text, only an icon.</p>

    <p>All of these classes can be used in conjunction with the regular button classes above.</p>
  </div>

  <p>
    <a href="#" class="button button__icon-left"><%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%> Search</a>
    <a href="#" class="button__success button__icon-left"><%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%> Search</a>
    <a href="#" class="button__secondary button__icon-right">Search <%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%></a>
    <a href="#" class="button__secondary button__icon"><%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%></a>
  </p>

  <pre class="sg-pre prettyprint">&lt;a href="#" class="button button__icon-left icon-search">&lt;%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%> Search&lt;/a>
&lt;a href="#" class="button__success button__icon-left icon-search">&lt;%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%> Search&lt;/a>
&lt;a href="#" class="button__secondary button__icon-right icon-search">Search &lt;%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%>&lt;/a>
&lt;a href="#" class="button__secondary button__icon icon-search">&lt;%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%>&lt;/a></pre>

  <p>Using <code>button__full</code> along with the <code>button__icon</code> classes allow you to create a centred, fullwidth button with an aligned icon:</p>

  <p>
    <a href="#" class="button button__full button__icon-left">
      <span class="button__icon-left">
        <%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%> Search
      </span>
    </a>
  </p>

  <pre class="sg-pre prettyprint">&lt;a href="#" class="button button__full">
  &lt;span class="button__icon-left">
    &lt;%= icon("search", stroke: "#ffffff") -%> Search
  &lt;/span>
&lt;/a></pre>

